stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Generated: Key created in TEE
    Generated --> Active: Sealed blob stored

    Active --> Archived: User archives key
    Archived --> Active: User unarchives key

    Active --> ExportRequested: User initiates export
    ExportRequested --> TwoFactorVerified: Email + Passkey confirmed
    ExportRequested --> Active: User cancels export

    TwoFactorVerified --> DelayPeriod: 24-hour timer starts
    TwoFactorVerified --> Active: User cancels export

    DelayPeriod --> Exported: Timer expires, export executed
    DelayPeriod --> Active: User cancels export

    Exported --> Active: Export complete

    note right of Archived
        Keys are never deleted
        archivedAt acts as soft-delete
    end note

    note right of DelayPeriod
        24-hour security delay
        User can cancel anytime
    end note

    note right of Exported
        One-time HPKE encryption
        to ephemeral recipient key
    end note
